---
title: Shawarma-Inspired Plant-Based Protein Shred Bowls with Veggies, Golden Rice and Garlic Toum
description: This plant-based dish will satisfy all your shawarma platter cravings! Complete with garlic toum, pickles and all the spices, this easy dinner hits the spot.

